# =============================================================================
# Patient Diet Orders CRUD
# =============================================================================

### Get patient diet order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/patient-diet-orders/<id>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get patient diet order by patient ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/patient-diet-orders/by-patient/7ea4e6ec-f359-485b-ac99-e0b44c3e18b9
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create patient diet order (assign diet to patient)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/patient-diet-orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "patientId": "<patient-id>",
    "dietOrderId": "<diet-order-id>"
}

### Delete patient diet order
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/patient-diet-orders/<id>
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

